content: With what I get today on this update, I cannot but give kudos to you. The time lapse did not peculiarly mattered, the outcome is what is essential. Thanks for this job. However on quick check on the book of Barnabas, I have two notices to make. In Chapter 4, where Exodus 31:18, Exodus 34:28 were quoted, only Exodus 3:18 opened as at press of button the two showed light together. The same thing happened in Chapter 6 where Ezekiel 11:19, Ezekiel 36:26 were quoted. Do check and correct. Thanks
The full stars are reserved till when the whole corrections are made. I love the work is why I do this review. But the only snag that remains is making the multiple references linkable appropriately.
Everything is great I just wish you would list what is Gnostic and what isn't, like what New Advent does and if you could, list which Fathers are Greek or Latin or otherwise, thanks.

love the app. it's quite readable and an amazing price for the content. I wish their was a way to change the organization do chronological order and a way to highlight/bookmark so only giving it 4 star.
